import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IOrganizationLikeDislike } from '../organization-like-dislike.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-organization-like-dislike-detail', templateUrl: './organization-like-dislike-detail.component.html', }) export class OrganizationLikeDislikeDetailComponent implements OnInit { organizationLikeDislike: IOrganizationLikeDislike | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ organizationLikeDislike }) => { this.organizationLikeDislike = organizationLikeDislike; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
